{"tid":1734591,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我妹妹比個賤男惹到有椰菜花","createTime":"2019-11-18T11:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T12:46:07.000Z","uid":102240,"like":7,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"aeae5084bafc46827583519f72c56216df0796ba","tid":1734591,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:10:44.000Z","msg":"我哋成個家族都崩潰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個唔係啲咩警世故事<br />\n係真人真事<br />\n我個妹先得嗰21歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前係大學識咗個師兄<br />\n上年同佢拍拖<br />\n我一見個男就覺得唔係好人<br />\n花花弗弗口甜舌滑嗰類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又成日借D意就帶佢去旅行<br />\n卒之真係出事<br />\n我個妹喊住同我講話驗到有椰菜花<br />\n我當堂O曬咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我阿媽知道後喊到崩潰<br />\n家吵屋閉咗好耐<br />\n而家我個妹日日都好唔開心<br />\n雖然醫生話有得醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我上網睇過係好難斷尾<br />\n咁就成世玩完啦<br />\n女仔真係要潔身自愛<br />\n帶眼識人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉...<br />\n我望住我個妹<br />\n作為家姐真係好無奈<br />\n唔知可以做啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df06c83cd22a1d804ccd8bf81193896afe431553","tid":1734591,"uid":53413,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"咩時勢呀<br />\n出左去未"},{"pid":"7869c18589a2c46dd24f8a2c5dec5ad6bfc95bfa","tid":1734591,"uid":38934,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"先達"},{"pid":"a6da25c1ee6c92b64030aa48f9a176e148200456","tid":1734591,"uid":66965,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"硬覺得係邊到見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tw 拉"},{"pid":"b4d18462c582c37520b45327da2a076485991efa","tid":1734591,"uid":284183,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:13:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家D女, 咁撚易比人中出, 又真係抵撚死既............</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"656e6bcbd980cfc2d32ba691bcd6a2c5f6ecb69b","tid":1734591,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:13:34.000Z","msg":"推!!!!!!!有冇可能理大裏面啲人開記招?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1733677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1733677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5029915433f13258e07047af36bb370afa3d2a30","tid":1734591,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"關香港人咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打緊仗"},{"pid":"1630ce954c647e8a890d52a7dd7002facbee80c4","tid":1734591,"uid":199925,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"唔洗整電話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560319c118f2daca981d8ce9ea5dfbf3a855c4a4","tid":1734591,"uid":10125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"是但喇<br />\n出咗去先"},{"pid":"a8e2d28baa99c1b95d83229d8c27c19e898a67f3","tid":1734591,"uid":242184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:14:04.000Z","msg":"比警犬屌咪會有椰菜花囉"},{"pid":"76a903575eea52195e451fb8dc7c5dbec57eabe2","tid":1734591,"uid":1425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"整左mon未"},{"pid":"e61c9eea4cc77c2f108a977febcf8b487ff7f83a","tid":1734591,"uid":102240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:14:22.000Z","msg":"講到咁又入感情台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"1bd232bd67f5282c60032881a2da8f093b625a52","tid":1734591,"uid":84277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:14:31.00